CustomField.description: The text to display on the confirm page for this form (Confirm page appears prior to entering the form and only for "non-invited" proposals, ie auto-assigned invites to allocations). If blank, confirm page is skipped.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: The text to display on the confirm page for this form (Confirm page appears prior to entering the form and only for "non-invited" proposals, ie auto-assigned invites to allocations). If blank, confirm page is skipped.
